                "answer": "Có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/026ad198-cefc-49d0-9312-5170b4a57c2d.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e0900d87-2787-4600-bc1a-60bab98371d2.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/da25a4c5-0971-449f-a45d-8e18c69ca7a4.png\"/>\n<br>Khi đó: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/f914fa8f-b5f0-4a0e-9bdf-cff4e0a30c8c.png\"/> hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ffd8265f-89f3-4196-8305-a87b7a94a90e.png\"/>\n<br>Thay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e78bcc91-6f9f-42d4-a6fa-c2f82ac93419.png\"/> vào <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/dead4c18-86fb-47c6-a83e-9db7491a0334.png\"/> ta được:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/cef5fb0b-5c5f-4bce-9473-959075dfc746.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/87da67b6-b940-4ef4-a084-74c0c122b517.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d26e7e88-4eaa-46e9-8dbf-c7e489488529.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/438838be-33a8-4ec5-ad64-9e722c72d9ba.png\"/>\n",
